nterest%20rates%20and%20deregulation%20are%20set%20to%20boost%20the%20asset%20class%2C%20the%20portfolio%20manager%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20shares%203%20trades%20for%20investors%20to%20boost%20returns%20outside%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBigger%20isn't%20always%20better.%20That's%20especially%20true%20regarding%20the%20stock%20market%20looking%20into%202025%2C%20according%20to%20Will%20Nasgovitz%2C%20CEO%20and%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20the%20%241.9%20billion%20Milwaukee-based%20value-investing%20firm%20Heartland%20Advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENasgovitz%20oversees%20various%20mid-cap%20and%20small-cap%20funds%20for%20the%20firm%2C%20and%20believes%20there%20are%20signs%20that%202025%20is%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20the%20year%20for%20small-caps%20and%20other%20unloved%20areas%20of%20the%20market%2C%20such%20as%20industrials%20and%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20just%20take%20his%20word%20for%20it%2C%20though.%20Small-caps%20are%20indeed%20trading%20at%20bargain%20prices%2C%20a%20reality%20reflected%20in%20meager%20portfolio%20allocations.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAllocations%20to%20small%20caps%20are%20very%2C%20very%20low%2C%26quot%3B%20Nasgovitz%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20at%20levels%20similar%20to%20the%20period%20in%20the%20late%2090s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENasgovitz%20isn't%20the%20only%20investor%20to%20draw%20comparisons%20between%20today's%20market%20and%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20dot-com%20bubble.%20Some%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20including%20top%20investor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-end-stages-of-major-tech-bubble-smead-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Smead%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20chief%20strategist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsp500-outlook-next-decade-forecast-david-kostin-goldman-stocks-strategist-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Kostin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20warned%20of%20concentration%20risk%20and%20soaring%20valuations%20among%20the%20biggest%20stocks%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20investors%20have%20overlooked%20small%20caps%20in%20favor%20of%20flashy%2C%20AI-fueled%20mega-cap%20tech%20companies%20with%20high%20valuations.%20Nasgovitz%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20small-cap%20S%26amp%3BP%20600%20index%2C%20which%20tracks%20the%20performance%20of%20US%20companies%20with%20a%20market%20capitalization%20between%20%241%20billion%20and%20%246.7%20billion%2C%20is%20currently%20trading%20at%2015.7x%20forward%20earnings%20%E2%80%94%20an%20almost%2040%25%20discount%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%2021.8x.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENasgovitz%20isn't%20fazed%20by%20low%20investor%20enthusiasm%20and%20valuations%20for%20small%20caps.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20he%20sees%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20buy%20in%20and%20unlock%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20low%20valuations%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20reasons%20Nasgovitz%20is%20bullish%20on%20smaller%20firms%20in%202025.%20One%20is%20that%20interest%20rates%20are%20on%20a%20downward%20trajectory%2C%20and%20small-cap%20companies%20are%20disproportionately%20set%20to%20benefit%20from%20an%20easing%20cycle.%20Lower%20interest%20rates%20mean%20lower%20borrowing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSmaller%20businesses%20rely%20more%20on%20variable%20rate%20debt%20with%20their%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20Nasgovitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20get%20a%20lowering%20of%20those%20rates%2C%20that%20should%20help%20them%20from%20a%20profit%20loss%20standpoint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20more%20friendly%20regulatory%20environment%20is%20also%20on%20the%20horizon%20as%20president-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20prepares%20to%20take%20office%2C%20Nasgovitz%20said.%20Small-cap%20stocks%20surged%20immediately%20after%20Trump's%20victory%20last%20November%20in%20anticipation%20of%20deregulation%20and%20protectionist%20policies%20for%20domestic%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeregulation%20will%20also%20boost%20M%26amp%3BA%20activity%2C%20providing%20another%20catalyst%20for%20small-cap%20valuations%2C%20he%20said.%20Nasgovitz%20anticipates%20that%20large%20caps%20and%20private%20equity%20firms%20alike%20will%20be%20eager%20to%20buy%20up%20small%20caps%2C%20bidding%20up%20valuations%20for%20small%20caps%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExposure%20to%20a%20small-cap%20index%20such%20as%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20600%20or%20Russell%202000%20can%20add%20diversity%20and%20an%20additional%20source%20of%20return%20to%20a%20portfolio%20skewed%20toward%20large%20caps.%20Examples%20of%20funds%20with%20small-cap%20exposure%20include%20the%20SPDR%20Portfolio%20S%26amp%3BP%20600%20Small%20Cap%20ETF%20(SPSM)%20and%20the%20iShares%20Russell%202000%20ETF%20(IWM).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299523322-8b99-4908-a38a-e119173bfea7%5C%22%3EIndustrials%20and%20Materials%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20small%20caps%2C%20Nasgovitz%20also%20likes%20a%20couple%20market%20sectors%20in%20particular%3A%20industrials%20and%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industrials%20sector%20has%20been%20challenged%20by%20contracting%20manufacturing%20activity%2C%20but%20Nasgovitz%20sees%20deregulation%20as%20a%20promising%20tailwind%20to%20jumpstart%20an%20industrials%20revival%20and%20is%20overweight%20on%20the%20sector.%20Nasgovitz%20also%20sees%20an%20opportunity%20in%20materials%2C%20a%20sector%20closely%20related%20to%20industrials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20industrials%20and%20materials%2C%20Nasgovtiz%20shared%20two%20stocks%20he's%20bullish%20on%3A%20aerospace%20composite%20manufacturer%20Hexcel%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fhxl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHXL%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20packaging%20company%20Sealed%20Air%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fsee-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEE%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAerospace%20companies%20like%20Boeing%20are%20preparing%20to%20upgrade%20their%20equipment%2C%20and%20Nasgovitz%20sees%20Hexcel%20as%20a%20major%20beneficiary.%20Nasgovtiz%20also%20sees%20Sealed%20Air%20benefiting%20from%20an%20improved%20industrial%20economy%20as%20packaging%20needs%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20investors%20are%20heeding%20Nasgovitz's%20warning%20regarding%20an%20overvalued%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20right%20now.%20Confidence%20in%20stocks%20is%20elevated%2C%20with%20over%2050%25%20of%20consumers%20expecting%20stock%20prices%20to%20increase%20in%20the%20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20last%20month's%20Consumer%20Confidence%20Survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bar%20is%20very%20high%20for%20stocks%20to%20meet%20those%20expectations%2C%20and%20that%20really%20points%20out%20the%20importance%20of%20doing%20your%20due%20diligence%2C%20being%20active%20and%20looking%20at%20the%20actual%20fundamentals%2C%20and%20zigging%20when%20others%20are%20zagging%2C%26quot%3B%20Nasgovtiz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20real%20pockets%20of%20opportunity%20that%20are%20off%20investors'%20radars%20because%20it's%20not%20AI%20in%20nature%2C%20it's%20not%20large%20cap%20in%20nature%2C%20yet%20business%20fundamentals%20or%20profit%20and%20evaluations%20are%20very%20compelling%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-cap-outperform-stock-market-industrials-trump-deregulation-value-investing-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736247602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677c20bd4fdf00939ed66003%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-cap-outperform-stock-market-industrials-trump-deregulation-value-investing-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Small-cap%20manager%20Will%20Nasgovitz%20shares%203%20tr