us%20immigration%20policies%2C%20global%20humanitarian%20commitments%2C%20and%20sharp%20criticisms%20from%20his%20rivals.%20The%20move%20also%20positions%20Conservative%20leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20as%20the%20frontrunner%20to%20take%20the%20reins%20of%20Canadian%20politics%2C%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20overhaul%20the%20immigration%20system%2C%20among%20several%20other%20proposed%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20Indian%20Canadians%2C%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20departure%20is%20%26quot%3Bbittersweet%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20immigration%20policies%20contributed%20to%20the%20challenges%20that%20ultimately%20led%20to%20his%20resignation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20driving%20without%20the%20right%20fuel%2C%26quot%3B%20Suraj%20Subhadarshee%2C%20business%20and%20product%20strategy%20manager%20at%20a%20tech%20firm%20in%20Toronto%2C%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BHis%20resignation%20was%20bittersweet.%20That%20said%2C%20some%20of%20his%20policies%20especially%20around%20immigration%2C%20government%20sanctions%20and%20aid%20have%20brought%20this%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20Canadian%20community%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20resignation.%20Although%20liberal%2C%20his%20government's%20policies%20have%20failed%20to%20avoid%20the%20economic%20setbacks%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20individuals%20and%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20a%20tech%20firm%20told%20NDTV%20under%20anonymity.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrudeau's%20Immigration%20Stand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau's%20immigration%20policies%20have%20been%20both%20celebrated%20and%20criticised.%20His%20government's%20ambitious%20targets%2C%20including%20plans%20to%20welcome%20over%20500%2C000%20permanent%20residents%20annually%20by%202025%2C%20were%20intended%20to%20address%20labour%20shortages%20and%20rejuvenate%20Canada's%20ageing%20population.%20However%2C%20critics%20argue%20that%20the%20rapid%20influx%20of%20immigrants%20has%20strained%20housing%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20other%20public%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20there%20was%20controlled%20immigration%20to%20some%20extent.%20But%2C%20the%20same%20period%20saw%20a%20huge%20influx%20of%20immigrants%20from%20around%20the%20globe.%20Bringing%20in%20immigrants%20in%20a%20controlled%20way%20is%20paramount%20to%20the%20success%20of%20a%20country's%20economy%20in%20the%20long-run%20but%20uncapped%20immigration%20involving%20government%20sanctions%20and%20other%20unrealistic%20benefits%20creates%20havoc.%20It's%20like%20a%20double-edged%20Swiss%20knife%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Subhadarshee%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmigration%20is%20important%20for%20Canada%20since%20the%20infrastructure%20seems%20to%20be%20crumbling%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20tech%20analyst.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20I%20am%20in%20Canada%2C%20I%20hope%20they%20stop%20all%20immigration%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia-Canada%20Relations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau's%20resignation%20also%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20future%20of%20India-Canada%20relations%2C%20which%20have%20reached%20a%20historic%20low.%20The%20Indian-Canadian%20community%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20implications%20of%20strained%20diplomatic%20ties%2C%20particularly%20for%20immigrants%20and%20those%20maintaining%20cross-border%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20I%20don't%20expect%20much%20from%20the%20interim%20government.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20definitely%20have%20high%20hopes%20from%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Conservatives%2C%20Pierre%20Poilievre%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Subhadarshee%20said.%20%26quot%3BImmigration%20has%20already%20been%20hit%20by%20and%20large.%20To%20be%20very%20transparent%2C%20any%20country%20that%20makes%20a%20law%20around%20immigration%20does%20it%20purely%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20it%20is%20no%20different%20in%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20stricter%20policies%20might%20deter%20some%20but%20could%20also%20restore%20a%20sense%20of%20fairness%20and%20sustainability%20to%20the%20system.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20policies%20were%20uncapped%2C%20this%20was%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20many%2C%20and%20now%20that%20the%20policies%20are%20leaning%20towards%20being%20stricter%20and%20stringent%2C%20I%20see%20people%20marching%20on%20roads%20and%20in%20and%20around%20government%20offices%2C%20which%20in%20my%20opinion%20is%20a%20disgrace.%20If%20one%20wants%20to%20live%20the%20Canadian%20dream%2C%20then%20one%20needs%20to%20earn%20it%20and%20not%20buy%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%20have%20been%20simmering%20since%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20September%202023%20allegation%20of%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20Nijjar%20was%20shot%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20Canada.%20India%20dismissed%20the%20accusation%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20claims%20that%20India%20sponsors%20criminal%20activities%20have%20drawn%20sharp%20criticism%20both%20domestically%20and%20internationally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHopefully%20the%20new%20reality%20of%20Canada%20will%20stabilise%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20starting%20with%20cleaning%20the%20house%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ruturaj%20Gaurav%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20a%20tech%20firm.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20resignation%20opens%20the%20possibility%20for%20a%20new%20leadership%20approach%20that%20could%20prioritise%20mending%20and%20strengthening%20bilateral%20relations%20with%20India.%20It%20will%20be%20good%20for%20some%20and%20tough%20for%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20Indian-Canadian%20software%20engineer%20under%20anonymity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Conservative%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPierre%20Poilievre%2C%20the%20Conservative%20leader%2C%20is%20a%20sharp%20critic%20of%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20immigration%20strategy.%20In%20December%202024%2C%20Poilievre%20stated%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bradical%2C%20out-of-control%20NDP-Liberal%20government%20has%20destroyed%20our%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20for%20a%20more%20measured%20approach%20to%20immigration.%20He%20has%20proposed%20capping%20immigration%20rates%20based%20on%20the%20availability%20of%20housing%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20had%20the%20privilege%20to%20meet%20Mr%20Poilievre%20in%20person%20and%20attend%20one%20of%20his%20closed-room%20meetings%2C%20and%20he%20seems%20to%20be%20very%20promising%20from%20what%20I%20have%20inferred.%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20high%20time%20we%20give%20a%20chance%20to%20the%20Conservatives.%20With%20Mr%20Poilievre%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20things%20might%20work%20in%20favour%20of%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Subhadarshee%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau's%20approach%20to%20immigration%20was%20a%20defining%20feature%20of%20his%20leadership.%20His%20government's%20initiatives%2C%20such%20as%20the%20resettlement%20of%20over%2040%2C000%20Syrian%20refugees%20and%20the%20Canada-Ukraine%20Authorization%20for%20Emergency%20Travel%20(CUAET)%20program%2C%20highlighted%20Canada's%20commitment%20to%20humanitarianism.%20The%20latter%20program%20allowed%20over%20200%2C000%20Ukrainians%20to%20seek%20temporary%20refuge%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20could%20be%20a%20shift%20toward%20prioritising%20skilled%20immigration%20tied%20directly%20to%20labour%20shortages%2C%20possibly%20reducing%20family%20reunification%20or%20refugee%20quotas.%20Mr%20Poilievre's%20focus%20on%20deregulation%20and%20reducing%20bureaucratic%20delays%20in%20housing%20development%20could%20accelerate%20solutions%20t