0Meddling%20In%20Europe%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20has%20lambasted%20Elon%20Musk%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20European%20politics%2C%20accusing%20the%20tech%20mogul%20of%20intervening%20directly%20in%20elections%20across%20the%20continent%2C%20including%20next%20month's%20snap%20federal%20polls%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20address%20on%20foreign%20policy%20in%20Paris%2C%20Macron%20didn't%20name%20Musk%20but%20made%20a%20pointed%20reference%20to%20the%20billionaire's%20actions%2C%20highlighting%20concerns%20over%20his%20alleged%20support%20for%20Germany's%20far-right%20AfD%20party.%20%26quot%3BWho%20could%20have%20imagined%2C%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20that%20the%20owner%20of%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20social%20networks%20would%20intervene%20directly%20in%20elections%2C%20including%20in%20Germany%3F%26quot%3B%20Macron%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fmacron-diplomacy-speech-trump-ukraine-731e5a1695f108a3fc87dd51be0ea3ee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20President%20targeted%20Musk%2C%20accusing%20the%20X%20owner%20of%20promoting%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20reactionary%20international%26quot%3B%20movement.%20Macron%20warned%20of%20the%20dangerous%20consequences%20of%20concentrating%20unchecked%20power%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few%20wealthy%20individuals%2C%20stressing%20the%20destabilising%20effect%20such%20power%20could%20have%20on%20democratic%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20AP%20report%2C%20Macron%20also%20perceived%20Musk's%20actions%20as%20a%20challenge%20to%20Europe's%20democratic%20values%20and%20unity%2C%20advocating%20for%20greater%20resilience%20in%20the%20face%20of%20external%20threats%20to%20the%20continent's%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20criticism%20of%20Musk%2C%