findia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fhmpv-cases-in-china-hmpv-symptoms-covid-19-flu-like-hmpv-cases%2Famp_articleshow%2F117022356.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fhmpv-cases-in-china-hmpv-symptoms-covid-19-flu-like-hmpv-cases%2Famp_articleshow%2F117022356.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fight%20HMPV%20With%20Nutrition%2C%20No%20Antibiotics%20Needed%3A%20Ex-AIIMS%20Director%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20role%20of%20antibiotics%20in%20treating%20the%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%2C%20a%20respiratory%20illness%20currently%20seeing%20an%20uptick%20in%20the%20country%2C%20said%20former%20AIIMS%20Director%20Dr%20Randeep%20Guleria%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20asking%20people%20to%20maintain%20proper%20hydration%2C%20and%20eat%20nutritious%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20IANS%2C%20Guleria%2C%20Chairman%2C%20Institute%20of%20Internal%20Medicine%2C%20Respiratory%20and%20Sleep%20Medicine%2C%20Medanta%20Gurugram%2C%20said%20the%20virus%20is%20not%20new%20and%20causes%20only%20mild%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHMPV%20is%20not%20novel%2C%20it's%20an%20old%20virus.%20It%20has%20been%20there%20for%20some%20time.%20Viruses%20usually%20cause%20mild%20illness%2C%20but%20in%20extremes%20of%20age%2C%20in%20infants%20and%20young%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%20or%20those%20with%20comorbidities%2C%20it%20can%20cause%20pneumonia%2C%20in%20young%20and%20old%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20breathing%20issues%2C%20as%20well%20as%20hospitalisation%2C%26quot%3B%20Guleria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20virus%20itself%20is%20usually%20self-limiting%2C%20and%20you%20just%20need%20symptomatic%20treatment.%20Take%20medicine%20for%20fever%2C%20keep%20hydration%2C%20and%20have%20good%20nutrition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20while%20asking%20people%20to%20avoid%20going%20to%20crowded%20places%20to%20curb%20the%20infection%20from%20spreading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20seven%20cases%20of%20HMPV%20--%20Karnataka%20(2)%2C%20Gujarat%20(1)%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20(2)%20have%20been%20reported.%20All%20the%20cases%20were%20detected%20in%20young%20children%20ranging%20from%203%20months%20old%20to%2013%20years%20old.%20However%2C%20it%20can%20occur%20in%20anyone%20because%20it%20is%20a%20droplet%20infection%20like%20influenza%2C%20said%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTreatment%20is%20mainly%20symptomatic.%20The%20need%20is%20to%20maintain%20good%20hydration%2C%20paracetamol%2C%20or%20any%20medication%20to%20decrease%20the%20fever%20and%20body%20aches.%20And%20if%20you%20have%20any%20other%20symptoms%20like%20cough%20and%20cold%2C%20an%20anti-allergic%20can%20be%20taken%20to%20decrease%20your%2C%20allergic%20symptoms%20like%20cold%20and%20cough%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20noted%20pulmonologist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20specific%20antiviral%20drug%20which%20should%20be%20taken.%20There%20is%20no%20role%20of%20taking%20antibiotics%20because%20it%20is%20a%20viral%20infection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20noting%20that%20infection%20control%20is%20very%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20advised%20people%20to%20regularly%20wash%20hands%20and%20maintain%20cough%20etiquettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736245140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fjgbribpo_hmpv-virus_650x400_06_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffight-hmpv-with-hydration-nutrition-no-antibiotics-needed-ex-aiims-director-dr-randeep-guleria-7419391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20no%20role%20of%20antibiotics%20in%20treating%20the%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%2C%20a%20respiratory%20illness%20currently%20seeing%20an%20u