cs%20and%20services%20provider%20through%20its%202021%20IPO%20and%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcvs-home-healthcare-signify-health-deal-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%248%20billion%20acquisition%20by%20CVS%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Datavant%20has%20stayed%20quiet%20in%20recent%20years%20about%20any%20fundraising%2C%20the%20outlet%20Buyouts%20reported%20in%20September%202023%20that%20New%20Mountain%20Capital%20was%20looking%20to%20extend%20its%20investment%20into%20Datavant%20through%20a%20continuation%20fund%20in%20a%20deal%20that%20would%20give%20Datavant%20additional%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmbrester%20didn't%20comment%20on%20the%20fundraising%20reports%20but%20acknowledged%20that%20Datavant's%20business%20maturation%20could%20lend%20itself%20to%20a%20public%20market%20debut.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20certainly%20at%20a%20size%20and%20scale%20where%20going%20public%20could%20be%20something%20that%20we%20contemplate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Datavant%20isn't%20feeling%20any%20short-term%20pressure%20from%20New%20Mountain%20or%20the%20rest%20of%20its%20board%20to%20make%20an%20IPO%20decision.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20plenty%20of%20cash%20on%20the%20balance%20sheet%20to%20do%20all%20the%20M%26amp%3BA%20I've%20just%20described%20and%20fund%20product%20roadmap%20investment%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Armbrester%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-unicorn-datavant-looking-for-healthcare-acquisition-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736244002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67786a159de00e389eb45c06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-unicorn-datavant-looking-for-healthcare-acquisition-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Health%20data%20unicorn%20Da