EMany%20advertisers%20in%20the%20current%20marketplace%20are%20demanding%20measurable%20results%20from%20their%20ads.%20Telly's%20general%20pitch%20is%20that%20it%20serves%20personalized%20ads%20on%20the%20second%20screen%20that%20encourage%20viewers%20to%20take%20action%20without%20interrupting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20bringing%20a%20new%20and%20innovative%20format%20to%20the%20big%20screen%20that's%20never%20been%20really%20utilized%20before%20with%20our%20dual-screen%20operating%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETelly%20has%20seen%20some%20interest%20from%20advertisers.%20In%20January%202024%2C%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.groupm.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fgroupm-forms-ad-innovation-accelerator-to-power-advertising-experiences-of-the-future%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20participant%20in%20WPP%20ad-buying%20giant%20GroupM's%20Ad%20Innovation%20Accelerator%20program.%20The%20group%20sought%20to%20create%20ad%20formats%20that%20could%20be%20distributed%20across%20TV%20platforms%20like%20Telly%2C%20Roku%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20more.%20Telly%20said%20it's%20worked%20on%20a%20pilot%20basis%20with%20several%20partners%20in%20categories%20like%20fast%20food%2C%20retail%2C%20and%20car%20insurance%2C%20mostly%20pulling%20from%20digital%20and%20video%20advertising%20budgets.%20It%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20share%20case%20studies%20from%20those%20partners%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20big%20fans%20of%20the%20innovation%20Telly%20is%20bringing%20to%20TV%2C%20both%20for%20consumers%20and%20advertisers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sam%20Bloom%2C%20head%20of%20partnerships%20at%20ad%20agency%20PMG%2C%20which%20has%20used%20Telly%20on%20behalf%20of%20advertising%20clients.%20%26quot%3BTelly's%20ability%20to%20transform%20the%20biggest%20screen%20in%20the%20home%20into%20a%20dynamic%20and%20measurable%20platform%20is%20a%20game%20changer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20obvious%20limitation%