s.%20The%20market%20is%20coming%20off%20back-to-back%20years%20with%20gains%20of%20more%20than%2023%25%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20outsized%20returns%2C%20driven%20largely%20by%20several%20mega-cap%20stocks%2C%20mean%20it's%20probably%20a%20good%20time%20to%20reassess%20and%20rebalance%20your%20holdings%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsp500-returns-outlook-decade-flat-returns-mike-wilson-morgan-stanley-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20CIO%20Mike%20Wilson%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20just%20let%20it%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20December%2023%20interview.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20get%20way%20out%20of%20bounds%2C%20you%20get%20way%20concentrated%20on%20certain%20things%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20you%20get%20in%20trouble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2032.5%25%2C%20the%20technology%20sector%20has%20by%20far%20the%20largest%20weighting%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20right%20now.%20And%20just%20the%20six%20largest%20companies%20in%20the%20index%20by%20market%20cap%20make%20up%20around%2030%25%20of%20it%2C%20according%20to%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221818%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22S%26amp%3BP%20500%20sector%20weights%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67773eeb59d276c1cdafde9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22830%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Global%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over-concentration%20in%20a%20portfolio%20can%20happen%20when%20any%20winning%20investments%20see%20big%20returns%2C%20not%20just%20when%20a%20certain%20sector%20fuels%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20portfolio%20is%20more%20concentrated%20than%20you%20want%20it%20to%20be%2C%20meaning%20it's%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20whims%20of%20its%20biggest%20holdings%2C%20there%20are%20multiple%20ways%20to%20rebalance%2C%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20might%20be%20constructing%20a%20portfolio%20with%20sector%20ETFs%2C%20weighting%20each%20according%20to%20their%20size%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20adjusting%20the%20positions%20as%20conditions%20evolve.%20When%20you're%20bullish%20on%20the%20utilities%20sector%20in%20particular%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you%20can%20overweight%20it.%20When%20you're%20bearish%20on%20consumer%20staples%2C%20you%20can%20underweight%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20is%20%26quot%3Bessentially%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20own%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20but%20I'm%20going%20to%20own%20it%20my%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20a%20view%20on%2C%20'Well%20this%20part%20of%20the%20index%20looks%20undervalued%2C%20this%20part%20of%20the%20index%20looks%20overvalued%2C%20or%20the%20trends%20that%20have%20been%20driving%20this%20performance%20are%20about%20to%20change%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Wilson's%20part%2C%20he%20likes%20the%20energy%20and%20materials%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20financial%20advisor%20or%20an%20investor%20who%20watches%20the%20market%20closely%20may%20be%20ideal%20for%20this%20strategy%2C%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20rebalancing%20strategy%20could%20be%20simply%20adding%20other%20index%20funds%20to%20current%20holdings%20instead%20of%20trimming%20them%2C%20according%20to%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20bring%20in%20new%20passive%20indices%20potentially%20that%20have%20underperformed%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20there's%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20equal-weighted%20index%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20standard%20market-cap-weighted%20index.%20Each%20constituent%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20equal-weighted%20index%20has%20the%20same%20size%20and%20impact%20on%20overall%20performance%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20cap-weighted%20index%20being%20dominated%20by%2C%20say%2C%20five%20or%2010%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20equal-weighted%20index%20is%20historically%20cheap%20relative%20to%20the%20cap-weighted%20index%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20underperformed%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20index%20funds%20that%20track%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20market%20include%20the%20Russell%202000%20for%20small-caps%20and%20the%20Vanguard%20Total%20Stock%20Market%20Index%20Fund%2C%20which%20holds%20more%20than%203%2C600%20US%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20concentration%20risk%20within%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20Wilson%20sees%20the%20broader%20index%20delivering%20poor%20annualized%20returns%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20He%20said%20he%20expects%20returns%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bflat-ish%26quot%3B%20during%20that%20period%20due%20to%20how%20high%20valuation%20levels%20are%20%E2%80%94%20namely%2C%20the%20Shiller%20CAPE%20ratio%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20forward%2012-month%20PE%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221678%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stock%20valuations%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6769b6e4e3e473ef263ad33a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%2C%20Rosenberg%20Research%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20very%20common%20view%2C%20that%20given%20where%20valuations%20are%20today%2C%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%20the%20returns%20from%20point%20A%20to%20point%20B%20will%20be%20basically%20flat-ish%2C%20and%20on%20a%20real%20basis%2C%20maybe%20negative%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20plenty%20of%20opportunities%20to%20make%20money%20over%20that%20time%20in%20sectors%20and%20stocks%20even%20if%20the%20index%20is%20flat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-strategy-stock-market-concentration-por