rce%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20schedule%20at%20a%20press%20meet%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20over%202%20lakh%20youngsters%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20this%20election.%20Announcing%20several%20initiatives%20to%20make%20the%20voting%20experience%20smooth%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20said%20arrangements%20would%20be%20made%20for%20the%20elderly%20and%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20to%20access%20polling%20booths%20without%20difficulty.%20It%20also%20said%20those%20above%2085%20years%20can%20cast%20their%20vote%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20asked%20party%20workers%20to%20go%20all-out%20in%20their%20preparations.%20%26quot%3BEven%20the%20biggest%20systems%20fail%20before%20your%20passion.%20You%20are%20our%20greatest%20strength.%20This%20is%20an%20election%20between%20the%20politics%20of%20work%20and%20the%20politics%20of%20abuses.%20We%20will%20surely%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20president%20welcomed%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20poll%20dates.%20%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20to%20choose%20a%20government%20that%20contributes%20to%20creation%20of%20a%20developed%20Delhi.%20BJP%20is%20committed%20to%20Delhi's%20all-round%20development%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20also%20dismissed%20allegations%20of%20manipulation%20of%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVM).%20He%20said%20EVMs%20are%20tamper-proof%20and%20hacking%20them%20is%20impossible.%20%26quot%3BEVMs%20are%20not%20hackable.%20Every%20claim%20of%20manipulation%20has%20been%20thoroughly%20investigated%20and%20debunked.%20This%20technology%20has%20consistently%20upheld%20the%20principles%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20also%20responded%20to%20allegations%20of%20manipulation%20of%20voter%20lists.%20Both%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20accused%20each%20other%20of%20getting%20names%20added%20and%20deleted%20from%20voter%20lists%20to%20boost%20poll%20prospects.%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20the%20Election%20Commission%20rigorously%20follows%20due%20process%20for%20any%20change%20in%20voter%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20is%20pushing%20hard%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20this%20election%2C%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20gone%20all%20out%20to%20turn%20the%20tables.%20Also%20in%20the%20fight%20is%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20going%20alone%20and%20targeting%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20AAP%20--%20its%20ally%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736243580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9ee01m08_pm-modi-arvind-kejriwal-split-_650x400_03_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-schedule-election-commission-announces-delhi-poll-dates-7418880%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20will%20vote%20on%20February%205%20to%20elect%20its%20new%20government%20and%20the%20counting%20is%20on%20February%208.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-schedule-election-commission-announces-delhi-poll-dates-7418880%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prashant%20Kishor%20Shifted%20To%20ICU%20As%20Health%20Worsens%20After%20Hunger%20Strike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJan%20Suraaj%20Party%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-prashant-kishor-was-arrested-and-why-he-was-on-indefinite-hunger-strike-at-gandhi-maidan-after-bpsc-paper-leak-7409467%5C%22%3EPrashant%20Kishor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20on%20Monday%20arrested%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20fast%20unto%20death%20and%20then%20released%20on%20%26quot%3Bunconditional%26quot%3B%20bail%2C%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Patna%20after%20his%20health%20deteriorated%20last%20night.%20He%20was%20later%20shifted%20to%20the%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit%20(ICU).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kishor%20was%20arrested%20from%20Patna's%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20early%20Monday%20morning%2C%20in%20pursuance%20of%20a%20case%20against%20him%20last%20week%20for%20holding%20'Aamaran%20anshan'%20(fast%20unto%20death)%20at%20Gandhi%20Maidan%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20a%20Patna%20High%20Court%20order%20that%20forbids%20any%20such%20demonstration%20at%20a%20place%20other%20than%20Gardani%20Bagh%20locality%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kishor%2C%20who%20was%20an%20election%20strategist%20before%20he%20plunged%20into%20politics%20full-time%2C%20was%20on%20an%20indefinite%20fast%20since%20January%202%20to%20back%20the%20civil%20service%20aspirants%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fbpsc-prelims-re-exam-sees-only-50-attendance-prashant-kishor-sent-to-judicial-custody-amid-protests-7412878%5C%22%3EBihar%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(BPSC)%20examination%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20held%20in%20December%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20Patna%20court%20Monday%20afternoon%2C%20which%20granted%20him%20bail%20with%20the%20condition%20that%2C%20he%20claimed%2C%20he%20must%20give%20a%20written%20undertaking%20not%20to%20take%20part%20in%20any%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20protest%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kishor%20and%20his%20legal%20team%20held%20that%20the%20condition%20was%20tantamount%20to%20%26quot%3Badmitting%20guilt%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20was%20then%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody.%20He%20was%20later%20released%20by%20the%20authorities%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrashant%20Kishor%20On%20Why%20He%20Rejected%20Bail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20outside%20the%20court%20last%20evening%2C%20Prashant%20Kishor%20explained%20why%20he%20refused%20to%20sign%20a%20bail%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20court%20and%20I%20was%20granted%20bail%20but%20in%20the%20bail%20order%20it%20was%20mentioned%20that%20I%20should%20not%20do%20any%20wrongdoings%2C%20so%20I%20rejected%20it%20and%20I%20accepted%20to%20go%20to%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20narrated%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20of%20Monday%20morning%3A%20%26quot%3BAround%204%20am%2C%20police%20reached%20Gandhi%20Maidan%2C%20where%20I%20have%20been%20sitting%20on%20an%20indefinite%20fast%20unto%20death%20for%20the%20last%20five%20days.%20They%20told%20me%20that%20they%20were%20detaining%20me%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20go%20with%20them.%20I%20left%20with%20them.%20Since%20my%20supporters%20were%20also%20with%20me%2C%20it's%20natural%20that%20a%20minor%20clash%20broke%20out%20(between%20them%20and%20the%20police).%20But%20by%20and%20large%2C%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20police%20was%20not%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20we%20left%20Gandhi%20Maidan%2C%20the%20police%20didn't%20tell%20me%20where%20they%20were%20taking%20me.%20They%20took%20me%20to%20AIIMS.%20I%20was%20there%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%20They%20refused%20to%20admit%20me%20and%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20why.%20The%20police%20then%20tried%20to%20take%20me%20to%20a%20different%20hospital%20but%20by%20then%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20my%20supporters%20had%20gathered%20at%20the%20gate%20of%20AIIMS.%20There%20was%20again%20a%20minor%20clash%20at%20the%20gate.%20From%20there%2C%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20police%20started%20deteriorating%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20he%20was%20made%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20police%20vehicle%20from%205%20am%20to%2011%20am%20and%20that%20they%20kept%20taking%20him%20to%20different%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20told%20me%20they%20would%20either%20take%20me%20to%20PMCH%20(Patna%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital)%20or%20NMCH%20(Nalanda%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital)%20but%20eventually%2C%20after%20five%20hours%2C%20they%20took%20me%20to%20Fatuha's%20community%20centre.%20They%20wanted%20to%20conduct%20my%20medical%20test%20and%20get%20a%20certificate%20from%20the%20doctors%20there.%20I%20refused%20to%20give%20my%20consent%20for%20that%20because%20I%20wasn't%20involved%20in%20any%20criminal%20activity.%20Police%20tried%20to%20convince%20the%20doctors%20for%20a%20certificate%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20give%20any%20such%20illegal%20certificate%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kishor%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20police%20argued%20that%20they%20had%20to%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Blonger%20route%20for%20crowd%20management%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736243520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Futgsmu1_prashant-kishor_625x300_07_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprashant-kishor-taken-to-hospital-as-health-worsens-after-hunger-strike-7417691%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jan%20Suraaj%20Party%20founder%20Prashant%20Kishor%2C%20who%20was%20on%20Monday%20arrested%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20fast%20unto%20death%20and%20then%20released%20on%20%26quot%3Bunconditional%26quot%3B%20bail%2C%20has%20been%20moved%20to%20the%20ICU%20after%20his%20health%20deteriorated%20last%20night.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprashant-kishor-taken-to-hospital-as-health-worsens-after-hunger-strike-7417691%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Disgraceful%20act'%3A%20Sam%20Konstas'%20mentor%20on%20Virat%20Ko