5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fenvironment%2Fb-20-summit-mark-carney-brookfield-asset-management-green-investment-for-global-climate-action-17644831.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20sees%20India%20as%20a%20major%20opportunity%20for%20investment%20due%20to%20its%20strong%20domestic%20demand%20and%20global%20supply%20chain%20shifts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EAnita%20Anand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnita%20Anand%2C%20Canada's%20Transport%20Minister%2C%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20more%20ambitious%20members%20of%20the%20Liberal%20caucus.%20With%20a%20background%20in%20financial%20market%20regulation%20and%20corporate%20governance%2C%20the%20Indian-origin%20leader%20has%20held%20several%20key%20positions%2C%20including%20overseeing%20public%20services%20and%20procurement%2C%20defence%2C%20and%20the%20Treasury%20Board%2C%20in%20the%20federal%20government.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLast%20year%2C%20Anita%20Anand%20announced%20stronger%20security%20measures%20for%20air%20passengers%20travelling%20to%20India.%20This%20came%20after%20tensions%20between%20Canada%20and%20India%20increased%20when%20Trudeau%20accused%20India%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%C2%A0in%20Canada.%20She%20said%20the%20security%20measures%20were%20for%20safety%20and%20included%20more%20checks%20for%20passengers%20flying%20from%20Canada%20to%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EDominic%20LeBlanc%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDominic%20LeBlanc%2C%20Canada's%20finance%20minister%2C%20stepped%20into%20the%20role%20immediately%20after%20Chrystia%20Freeland's%20resignation%20and%20is%20one%20of%C2%A0Trudeau's%20closest%20allies.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLeBlanc%20is%20a%20trusted%20ally%20of%20Trudeau.%20Their%20long-standing%20friendship%20includes%20LeBlanc%20babysitting%20Trudeau%20and%20his%20siblings%20in%20their%20youth.%20LeB