0conference%20today%20to%20announce%20the%20dates%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20that%20EVMs%20have%20repeatedly%20passed%20the%20test%20of%20judicial%20scrutiny%20and%20have%20earned%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20nation's%20highest%20courts%20on%2042%20separate%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20polls%20are%20set%20to%20be%20held%20on%20February%205%20and%20the%20counting%20is%20scheduled%20for%20February%208.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20said%20that%20EVMs%20are%20tamper-proof%2C%20rendering%20rigging%20and%20hacking%20impossible.%20He%20described%20allegations%20of%20tampering%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%20and%20stressed%20that%20the%20ECI%20has%20always%20prioritised%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEVMs%20are%20not%20hackable.%20Every%20claim%20of%20manipulation%20has%20been%20thoroughly%20investigated%20and%20debunked.%20This%20technology%20has%20consistently%20upheld%20the%20principles%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%20%26quot%3BOn%2042%20different%20occasions%2C%20the%20judiciary%20has%20reaffirmed%20trust%20in%20EVMs.%20These%20machines%20represent%20years%20of%20technological%20evolution%20and%20are%20a%20matter%20of%20national%20pride.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20also%20addressed%20concerns%20regarding%20alleged%20manipulation%20of%20voter%20lists%2C%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20become%20a%20major%20point%20of%20contention%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections.%20Political%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20have%20alleged%20discrepancies%20in%20voter%20rolls%2C%20claiming%20wrongful%20deletions%20and%20additions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20these%20allegations%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20stressed%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20rigorously%20follows%20due%20process%20for%20any%20changes%20in%20voter%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20preparation%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20is%20a%20transparent%20process%20involving%20political%20parties%20at%20every%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20allegations%20are%20baseless.%20Disclosure%20is%20our%20main%20pillar%2C%20and%20detailed%20guidelines%20and%20datasets%20are%20available%20on%20our%20website.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20added%20that%20the%20ECI%20ensures%20full%20disclosure%20and%20provides%20opportunities%20for%20objections%20throughout%20the%20process.%20%26quot%3BAll%20deletions%20and%20additions%20are%20done%20following%20the%20due%20process%20of%20law.%20There%20is%20no%20room%20for%20manipulation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20orchestrating%20deletions%20in%20constituencies%20where%20it%20has%20a%20strong%20voter%20base.%20AAP%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20had%20claimed%20in%20December%20that%20the%20BJP%20sought%20to%20remove%20over%2011%2C000%20names%20from%20the%20voter%20list%20in%20the%20Shahdara%20Assembly%20segment.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20also%20alleged%20that%20a%20similar%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20was%20underway%20in%20his%20own%20constituency%2C%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20denied%20these%20allegations%2C%20countering%20that%20AAP%20has%20been%20adding%20fake%20names%20to%20voter%20lists%20to%20inflate%20its%20support%20base.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736241540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fchs1ahkg_rajiv-kumar-_625x300_07_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-2025-delhi-elections-date-no-drawback-in-evms-not-going-back-to-paper-ballots-poll-commissioner-7418796%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20today%20dismissed%20allegations%20o