%20based%20on%20tipping%20conventions%2C%20while%20the%20cashier%20would%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20a%20subset%20of%20workers%20would%20stand%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20proposal.%20The%20Yale%20Budget%20Lab%20studied%20who%20would%20be%20impacted%20by%20eliminating%20taxes%20on%20tips.%20Tipped%20workers%20tended%20to%20skew%20younger%2C%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbudgetlab.yale.edu%2Fnews%2F240624%2Fno-tax-tips-act-background-tipped-workers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJune%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Census%20Bureau%20data%20from%20Tedeschi.%20The%20median%20tipped%20worker%20in%202023%20was%2031%20years%20old%2C%20and%20a%20third%20of%20tipped%20workers%20were%20under%20the%20age%20of%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fd7tYo%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Share%20of%20each%20age%20group%20reporting%20tipped%20income%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Yale%20Budget%20Lab%20also%20looked%20at%20what%20roles%20and%20industries%20tipped%20workers%20are%20concentrated%20in.%20Across%20industries%2C%20restaurants%20and%20other%20food%20services%20had%20the%20greatest%20share%20of%20total%20tips%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20unsurprising%2C%20considering%20how%20compensation%20is%20generally%20structured%20in%20that%20industry.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20median%20pay%20for%20food%20and%20beverage%20serving%20and%20related%20workers%20was%20%2414.29%20per%20hour%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fooh%2Ffood-preparation-and-serving%2Ffood-and-beverage-serving-and-related-workers.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-wi