ote%20BofA%20Securities%20analysts%20in%20a%20Monday%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20rally%20has%20faltered%2C%20with%20Chinese%20stocks%20posting%20their%20worst%20start%20to%20a%20year%20in%20nearly%20a%20decade%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20trading%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strength%20and%20scope%20of%20China's%20policies%20are%20taking%20time%20to%20flow%20through%20the%20system%2C%20so%20their%20impact%20on%20GDP%20and%20earnings%20will%20lag%20for%20quarters%2C%20wrote%20the%20BofA%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20benchmark%20CSI300%20is%20down%203.5%25%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20while%20Hong%20Kong's%20Hang%20Seng%20Index%20is%20down%203.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20CSI300%20index%20closed%200.7%25%20higher.%20The%20Hang%20Seng%20closed%201.2%25%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20yuan%20also%20hit%20a%2016-month%20low%20on%20Monday%2C%20fueled%20by%20investor%20jitters%20ahead%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20January%2020.%20Trump%20has%20threatened%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20of%2060%25%20on%20Chinese%20imports%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b960a3a-2ba4-4c12-8bcd-e1c88bdce44e%5C%22%3EGeopolitical%20risks%20are%20already%20playing%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20designated%20two%20high-profile%20tech%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20Tencent%20and%20CATL%20%E2%80%94%20as%20Chinese%20military%20companies%20operating%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETencent%20is%20a%20tech%20giant%20known%20for%20its%20WeChat%20super%20app%2C%20while%20CATL%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20battery%20maker%20and%20a%20major%20supplier%20to%20EV%20maker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20134%20companies%20on%20the%20Pentagon's%20blacklist%20aren't%20sanctioned%20but%20being%20on%20the%20list%20could%20discourage%20other%20American%20firms%20from%20doing%20business%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETencent%20and%20CATL%20shares%20declined%20sharply%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20strong%20double-digit%20gains%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Tencent%20and%20CATL%20have%20pushed%20back%20on%20the%20designation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTencent's%20inclusion%20on%20this%20list%20is%20clearly%20a%20mistake.%20We%20are%20not%20a%20military%20company%20or%20supplier%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Tencent%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20list%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20impact%26quot%3B%20on%20Tencent's%20business%20unlike%20sanctions%20or%20export%20controls%2C%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bwill%20nonetheless%20work%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20to%20address%20any%20misunderstanding%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Tencent%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20CATL%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bhas%20never%20engaged%20in%20any%20military-related%20business%20or%20activities%2C%20so%20this%20designation%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20is%20a%20mistake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20proactively%20engage%20with%20DoD%20to%20address%20the%20false%20designation%2C%20including%20legal%20action%20if%20necessary%2C%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20our%20company%20and%20shareholders%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20CATL%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECATL%2C%20which%20has%20a%20market%20share%20of%20about%2040%25%20in%20the%20global%20EV%20cell%20market%2C%20said%20it%20expects%20the%20designation%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Bno%20substantially%20adverse%20impact%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20designation%20of%20Chinese%20firms%20on%20the%20US%20military%20blacklist%20is%20a%20foreboding%20sign%20that%20%26quot%3Btensions%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20watered%20down%20anytime%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Yeap%20Jun%20Rong%2C%20a%20market%20strategist%20