0these%20sections%20would%20tilt%20the%20balance%20in%20the%20five%20crucial%20swing%20states%20in%20favour%20of%20Kamala%20Harris%20who%2C%20the%20pundits%20felt%2C%20had%20run%20a%20%E2%80%9Cflawless%20campaign.%E2%80%9D%20At%20this%20point%2C%20various%20opinion%20polls%20were%20produced%20to%20show%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20the%20least%20acceptable%20candidate.%20Trump's%20pariah%20status%20was%20garnished%20by%20pious%20comments%20centred%20on%20the%20belief%20that%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20women%20attached%20greater%20priority%20to%20reproductive%20rights%20over%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy.%20If%20these%20pious%20certitudes%20appear%2C%20in%20hindsight%2C%20to%20be%20quite%20ridiculous%2C%20the%20underlying%20humour%20behind%20the%20meltdown%20once%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20Trump%20had%20beaten%20Harris%20conclusively%2C%20was%20inescapable.%20The%20political%20analysts%20moved%20from%20analysing%20the%20votes%20to%20debunking%20the%20intelligence%20of%20voters%20and%20lamenting%20the%20future%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20global%20liberal%20fraternity%20failed%20to%20anticipate%20the%20underlying%20support%20for%20Trump%20and%20needed%20%E2%80%98safe%20zones'%20and%20counselling%20on%20the%20campuses%20to%20get%20over%20the%20trauma%20of%20an%20unpalatable%20electoral%20verdict%2C%20much%20of%20the%20responsibility%20lies%20with%20the%20pollsters.%20In%20poll%20after%20poll%2C%20these%20so-called%20independent%20pollsters%20had%20suggested%20that%20the%20outcome%20on%20November%205%20was%20within%20the%20margin%20of%20error%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20too%20close%20to%20call.%20Was%20this%20due%20to%20sampling%20errors%20or%20social%20pressures%20that%20made%20those%20who%20voted%20for%20Trump%20wary%20of%20admitting%20this%20openly%3F%20This%20was%20certainly%20the%20case%20in%20the%202016%20presidential%20election%2C%20and%20it%20speaks%20volumes%20for%20the%20political%20environment%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20democracy%2C%20that%20supporters%20of%20the%20winner%20have%20to%20keep%20their%20preferences%20under%20wraps%20for%20fear%20of%20social%20ostracism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20From%20Trump's%20Victory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victory%20of%20Trump%20should%2C%20ideally%2C%20be%20a%20lesson%20to%20the%20presiding%20deities%20of%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98legacy%20media'%20and%20the%20polling%20industry%20to%20review%20their%20political%20assumptions.%20But%20the%20lessons%20aren't%20necessarily%20limited%20to%20the%20US.%20The%20three%20sets%20of%20elections%20held%20last%20year%20in%20India%20also%20warranted%20a%20clinical%20post-mortem%20which%2C%20alas%2C%20has%20not%20been%20forthcoming.%20Instead%2C%20the%20mismatch%20between%20what%20was%20projected%20and%20what%20transpired%20has%20been%20brushed%20aside%20casually%2C%20till%20the%20blunder%20the%20next%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20lesson%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20and%20the%20subsequent%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20is%20the%20diminishing%20faith%20in%20pollsters.%20Most%20polls%20predicted%20a%20resounding%20BJP%20win%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20win%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20Haryana%20and%20a%20small%20advantage%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20formation%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20pollsters%20failed%20to%20anticipate%20the%20big%20setbacks%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Haryana.%20Likewise%2C%20the%20BJP%20victory%20in%20the%20Odisha%20assembly%20was%20unanticipated.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Haryana%20and%20its%20clean%20sweep%20in%20Maharashtra%20went%20against%20prevailing%20conventional%20wisdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20entirely%20possible%20that%20the%20main%20problem%20with%20Indian%20polling%20outfits%20is%20shoddy%20or%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20non-existent%20fieldwork.%20To%20pursue%20a%20truly%20random%20sampling%2C%20as%20demanded%20by%20statisticians%2C%20is%20both%20time-consuming%20and%20expensive.%20Instead%2C%20what%20is%20being%20pursued%20is%20either%20telephone%20polls%20of%20questionable%20authenticity%20or%20findings%20based%20almost%20entirely%20on%20the%20judgments%20of%20a%20new%20breed%20of%20political%20analysts.%20Since%20many%20of%20those%20in%20media%20organisations%20and%20political%20parties%20are%20untutored%20in%20the%20art%20of%20analysing%20poll%20findings%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20for%20a%20growing%20tribe%20of%20charlatans%20to%20pull%20the%20wool%20over%20the%20eyes%20of%20their%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Introspection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20actual%20results%2C%20there%20has%20hardly%20been%20any%20known%20instance%20of%20those%20who%20commission%20opinion%20(and%20exit)%20polls%20doing%20a%20post-mortem%20of%20the%20quantum%20of%20variation%20with%20the%20actual%20results.%20This%20suggests%20that%20the%20errors%20(methodological%20or%20wilful)%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20fraud%2C%20will%20be%20repeated%20in%20the%20next%20round%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnless%20media%20organisations%20develop%20a%20culture%20of%20accountability%20to%20their%20consumers%2C%20they%2C%20too%2C%20will%20experience%20the%20same%20ridicule%20that%20has%20been%20heaped%20on%20their%20liberal%20counterparts%20by%20the%20growing%20tribe%20of%20irreverent%20YouTubers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20party%20that%20experienced%20the%20most%20strategic%20setback%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%2C%20it%20is%20to%20be%20expected%20that%20the%20BJP%20must%20have%20undertaken%20the%20most%20rigorous%20post-poll%20dissection%20to%20understand%20where%20it%20went%20wrong%20and%20what%20remedial%20steps%20to%20take.%20On%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20the%20findings%20of%20such%20an%20exercise%20have%20not%20been%20made%20public%2C%20and%20the%20promised%20%E2%80%98chintan'%2C%20if%20any%2C%20has%20been%20conducted%20behind%20closed%20doors.%20Although%20the%20internal%20assessments%20of%20the%20BJP%20haven't%20been%20made%20public%2C%20certain%20broad%20conclusions%20are%20in%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Modi%20Cult%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20while%20it%20is%20understandable%20the%20BJP%20tried%20to%20turn%20a%20parliamentary%20election%20into%20a%20presidential%20election%2C%20there%20were%20significant%20distortions.%20The%20personality%20cult%20around%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20centred%20almost%20exclusively%20on%20the%20report%20card%20of%20the%20past%20decade.%20What%20was%20on%20offer%20in%20the%20coming%20five%20years%E2%80%94apart%20from%20the%20generalities%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%E2%80%94was%20not%20spelt%20out%20in%20any%20detail.%20It%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20specifics%20that%20made%20the%20campaign%20skewed.%20This%20meant%20that%20pressing%20local%20grievances%20were%20either%20given%20the%20go-by%2C%20as%20happened%20in%20central%20and%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Alternatively%2C%20flawed%20local%20inputs%20compelled%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20focus%20exclusively%20on%20local%20issues%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20national%20outlook.%20Somehow%2C%20the%20BJP%20couldn't%20manage%20to%20strike%20an%20equilibrium%20between%20the%20Modi%20cult%2C%20the%20future%20and%20local%20complications.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20local%20units%20were%20overawed%20by%20the%20force%20and%20intensity%20of%20the%20national%20projection%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlush%20With%20Resources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20as%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20was%20not%20expected%20to%20suffer%20from%20any%20resource%20crunch.%20However%2C%20what%20was%20experienced%20on%20the%20ground%20was%20the%20precise%20opposite.%20The%20BJP%20campaign%20was%20inundated%20with%20resources%2C%20much%20more%20than%20could%20be%20effectively%20managed.%20This%20meant%20that%20the%20focus%20of%20many%20campaigning%20teams%20became%20pecuniary%20rather%20than%20political.%20Rather%20than%20chasing%20votes%2C%20many%20campaigners%20chased%20campaign%20funds.%20In%20winnable%20seats%2C%20there%20was%20often%20a%20schism%20between%20the%20candidate%20and%20the%20organisation.%20In%20seats%20where%20the%20prospects%20were%20more%20distant%2C%20the%20focus%20was%20often%20on%20cost-cutting%20to%20maximise%20non-productive%20surplus.%20This%20was%20particularly%20so%20in%20states%20where%20the%20BJP%20doesn't%20have%20an%20entrenched%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20unintended%20consequence%20of%20this%20superabundance%20of%20resources%20was%20that%20the%20traditional%20election%20strategy%20of%20maximising%20involvement%20in%20the%20outreach%20to%20the%20voters%20was%20compromised%20in%20favour%20of%20impersonal%20razzmatazz%20that%20limited%20involvement.%20There%20are%20reasons%20to%20believe%20that%20in%20many%20regions%2C%20there%20was%20a%20frostiness%20between%20the%20BJP%20organisation%20and%20the%20wider%20saffron%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrassroots%20Tell%20A%20Different%20Story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20if%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20grassroots%20is%20any%20indication%2C%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20suffered%20on%20account%20of%20the%20leadership's%20over-reliance%20on%20political%20management%20consultancies%20who%20were%20entrusted%20with%20responsibilities%20ranging%20from%20advising%20on%20candidate%20selection%20to%20campaign%20feedback.%20While%20creating%20a%20channel%20that%20is%20independent%20of%20the%20party%20organisation%20creates%20alternative%20inputs%2C%20there%20are%20two%20dangers.%20First%2C%20the%20perceived%20importance%20of%20consultants%20can%20lead%20to%20the%20local%20party%20organisation%20retreating%20into%20a%20shell%20and%20becoming%20less%20active.%20Secondly%2C%20if%20the%20consultants%20fail%20to%20pick%20up%20important%20local%20trends%2C%20whether%20because%20of%20inexperience%20or%20ineptitude%2C%20the%20overall%20campaign%20can%20suffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20know%2C%20for%20example%2C%20whether%20the%20BJP%20misread%20the%20quantum%20of%20local%20anger%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20Varanasi%20over%20the%20civic%20improvements.%20Moreover%2C%20was%20the%20party%20aware%20of%20the%20silent%20campaign%20centred%20on%20its%20supposed%20plan%20to%20scrap%20reservations%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%20allying%20itself%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Muslim-Yadav%20combination%20in%20Awadh%20and%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0It%20is%20entirely%20possible%20that%20rather%20than%20washing%20dirty%20linen%20in%20public%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20quietly%20gone%20about%20the%20task%20of%20taking%20remedial%20measures%2C%20and%20without%20public%20recriminations.%20After%20all%2C%20within%20a%20span%20of%20a%20few%20months%2C%20the%20party%20managed%20to%20retain%20Haryana%2C%20a%20state%20from%20which%20it%20had%20been%20written%20off%20after%20the%20parliamentary%20election.%20Much%20more%20significant%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20criticism%20levelled%20against%20it%20for%20accommodating%20disreputable%20defectors%20and%20consequently%20losing%20the%20plot%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%2C%20the%20BJP%20stuck%20to%20the%20same%20alliance%20and%20won%20the%20Assembly%20election%20resoundingly.%3Cbr%3E%5CnNo%20doubt%20caste%20alignments%20and%20leadership%20issues%20played%20their%20usual%20part%20in%20the%20BJP's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20both%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20all%20reports%20suggested%20an%20energised%20grassroots%20campaign%20that%20involved%20personalised%20contact%20with%20the%20electorate.%20This%20implies%20that%20the%20relative%20indifference%20of%20the%20party's%20support%20and%20activist%20base%E2%80%94%20a%20feature%20of%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%E2%80%94was%20absent%20in%20the%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Indian%20Voters%20Are%20Unique%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%20and%20North%20America%2C%20voting%20behaviour%20invariably%20follows%20a%20social%20pattern.%20People%20vote%20as%20individuals%20but%20their%20individual%20preference%20is%20coloured%20by%20their%20ethnicity%2C%20income%2C%20education%20and%20gender.%20All%20these%20factors%20are%20present%20in%20India%2C%20with%20caste%20often%20taking%20the%20place%20of%20ethnicity%20and%20class%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20an%20additional%20complication.%20The%20state%20of%20a%20political%20organisation%20or%20network%20in%20the%20constituencies%20plays%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20determining%20electoral%20outcomes.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20passive%20support%20for%20parties%2C%20its%20translation%20into%20actual%20votes%20also%20depends%20on%20local%20triggers.%20The%20relative%20importance%20of%20local%20alignments%20varies%20from%20state%20to%20state.%20In%20states%20such%20as%20West%20Bengal%2C%20it%20is%20overwhelming%2C%20while%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20it%20is%20low.%20There%20was%20an%20electoral%20malfunction%20in%20the%20BJP%20machinery%20in%20a%20few%20states%20that%20cost%20the%20party%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20majority.%20This%20was%20addressed%20in%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%2C%20such%20that%20they%20prompted%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20was%20a%20black%20swan%20event.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0Such%20a%20conclusion%2C%20of%20course%2C%20would%20exonerate%20the%20pollsters%20from%20the%20grave%20charge%20of%20professional%20incompetence.%20The%20need%20for%20such%20generosity%20is%20unwarranted%20since%20the%20pollsters%20imagined%20they%20were%20swimming%20with%20the%20tide.%20They%20will%20continue%20to%20think%20that%20victory%20belongs%20to%20those%20who%20shout%20the%20loudest.%20For%20more%20discerning%20analysts%2C%20however%2C%20it%20will%20be%20necessary%20to%20blend%20the%20quantitative%20with%20an%20understanding%20of%20how%20the%20ground%20situation%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERespect%20The%20Voter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20before%20November%205%2C%20a%20pollster%20with%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20%E2%80%98gold%20standard'%20released%20a%20dramatic%20finding%20that%20in%20Iowa%2C%20a%20strong%20Republican%20state%2C%20Harris%20would%20beat%20Trump%2047%25%20to%2044%25.%20She%20detected%20a%20late%20swing%20of%20older%20women%20towards%20the%20Democrats%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20reproductive%20rights.%20The%20poll%20raised%20hopes%20among%20Harris%20supporters%20of%20a%20landslide%20win%20nationally.%20When%20the%20votes%20were%20counted%2C%20it%20revealed%20that%20the%20pollster%20was%20off%20the%20mark%20by%20a%20whopping%2016%20points.%20Trump%20won%2056%25%20of%20the%20votes%20to%20Harris's%2042.7%25.%20It%20wasn't%20even.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20pollster%20in%20Iowa%20has%20since%20shut%20shop%20and%20changed%20professions.%20However%2C%20what%20is%20one%20to%20make%20of%20the%20polling%20agencies%20that%20suggested%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20win%2025%20seats%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20between%20eight%20and%2010%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3F%20By%20that%20logic%2C%20the%20BJP%20tally%20in%202024%20would%20have%20crossed%20400.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%2012%20in%20Bengal%20and%20none%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20lessons%20from%202024%3A%20discount%20(but%20don't%20totally%20disregard)%20the%20pollsters%2C%20and%20keep%20a%20sharp%20eye%20on%20politics%20on%20the%20ground.%20Respect%20the%20judgment%20of%20voters.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20their%20instincts%20aren't%20way%20off%20the%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%C2%A0Distinguished%20Fellow%2C%20India%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3