%80%9CI%20haven%E2%80%99t%20saved%20anything%20for%20myself.%20All%20I%20do%20right%20now%20is%20for%20them%20and%20their%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNoori%20%3Cem%3Eaaya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grandma)%20has%20always%20prioritised%20education%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20study%20three%20degrees%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Naga%20Thejas%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20at%20SIP%20Memorial%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20social%20work%2C%20hoping%20to%20start%20his%20own%20NGO%20to%20support%20people%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20600px)%20100vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Activities%20conducted%20for%20the%20children%20at%20the%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust%20provides%20a%20comfortable%20home%20for%20children%20who%20have%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20comfortable%20at%20SIP%20home%20as%20I%20used%20to%20get%20healthy%20and%20delicious%20meals%20every%20day.%20I%20also%20had%20my%20friends%2C%20with%20whom%20time%20would%20fly%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naga%2C%20sharing%20the%20joy%20