%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epiggery%2C%20and%20sericulture%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202003-04%2C%20he%20embraced%20horticulture%20as%20well%20with%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20horticulture%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20nursery%20has%2070%2C000-75%2C000%20saplings%2C%20and%20is%20dedicated%20to%20training%20other%20farmers.%20His%20focus%20is%20on%20helping%20his%20fellow%20farmers%20adopt%20better%20practices%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20farm%20expanded%20in%20both%20size%20and%20productivity%2C%20and%20he%20continued%20to%20experiment%20with%20new%20crops%2C%20including%20pineapples%20and%20other%20fruits.%20He%20also%20travelled%20to%20places%20like%20Odisha%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20with%20the%20horticulture%20department%20of%20Assam%2C%20to%20study%20advanced%20farming%20practices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarbeshwar%E2%80%99s%2032-year-old%20nephew%2C%20Purno%20Boro%2C%20a%20dedicated%20farmer%2C%20has%20been%20learning%20extensively%20from%20him%20and%20applying%20those%20lessons%20to%20his%20own%2016-acre%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CBananas%20are%20a%20major%20crop%20on%20my%20farm%2C%20but%20I%20also%20grow%20papayas%20and%20areca%20nuts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Purno%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20found%20that%20by%20using%20intercropping%20techniques%20year-round%2C%20our%20profits%20nearly%20double.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20passionate%20learner%2C%20he%20regularly%20watches%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20expand%20his%20knowledge.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20secure%20a%20government%20job%2C%20farming%20became%20the%20best%20option%20for%20me.%20Having%20someone%20like%20Sarbeshwar%20to%20guide%20me%20has%20been%20crucial%20in%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20stability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20For%20the%20upcoming%20season%2C%20Purno%20has%20planted%20cacao%20on%20four%20acres%2C%20intercropped%20with%20areca%20palm%20trees%2C%20and%20has%20also%20introduced%20king%20c