%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20person%20who%20accidentally%20hit%20the%20dog%20did%20not%20do%20so%20on%20purpose.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20help%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20too.%20But%20he%20did%20not%20see%20the%20dog%20during%20the%20night%20and%20he%20was%20guiltridden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20by%20this%20experience%2C%20Rimjhim%20found%20a%20way%20to%20address%20this%20issue.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20simple%20desire%20to%20make%20roads%20safer%20for%20animals%20and%20people%20alike%2C%20has%20now%20turned%20into%20Pawsitivity%20%E2%80%94%20a%20successful%20venture%20focused%20on%20manufacturing%20QR-enabled%20reflective%20collars%20for%20stray%20animals%2C%20all%20made%20by%20a%20team%20of%20underprivileged%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20simple%20solution%20with%20a%20big%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20started%20making%20the%20collars%20in%202016%2C%20the%20concept%20to%20design%20a%20reflective%20collar%20that%20could%20be%20worn%20by%20stray%20animals%20to%20make%20them%20more%20visible%20to%20drivers%20at%20night%20was%20simple.%20However%2C%20creating%20this%20collar%20required%20an%20insight%20into%20the%20industry%20that%20she%2C%20as%20a%20teacher%2C%20did%20not%20have.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20she%20started%20making%20the%20reflective%20collars%20for%20Pawsitivity%20and%20interacting%20with%20the%20dogs%20that%20Rimjhim%20and%20her%20husband%20Tushar%20would%20take%20care%20of%2C%20she%20softened%20a%20bit.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20I%20was%20earning%20a%20significant%20amount%20every%20month%20by%20working%20for%20these%20animals.%20It%20was%20only%20fair%20that%20I%20gave%20some%20love%20back.%20So%2C%20I%20began%20befriending%20and%20feeding%20them.%20Some%20people%20might%20not%20like%20it%2C%20but%20I%20do%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20%3Cem%3Edidi%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Rimjhim%E2%80%99s)%20company%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20work%20in%20fewer%20houses%2C%20and%20could%20spend%20more%20time%20on%20my%20own.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20lacked%20the%20knowledge%20of%20where%20to%20source%20the%20materials%20or%20who%20could%20manufacture%20the%20collars.%20It%20was%20Reena%2C%20her%20house%20help%20at%20the%20time%2C%20who%20stepped%20in.%20She%20suggested%20where%20they%20could%20find%20the%20necessary%20materials%20and%20mentioned%20that%20she%20had%20some%20basic%20stitching%20skills%20that%20could%20come%20in%20handy.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20worked%20together%2C%20and%20the%20very%20first%20batch%20of%20collars%20that%20we%20made%2C%20we%20made%20with%20her%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rimjhim%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReena%20Dhanak%2C%2035%2C%20from%20a%20small%20settlement%20near%20Indore%2C%20has%20her%20own%20unique%20journey%20in%20animal%20welfare.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20was%20always%20against%20having%20dogs%20loitering%20outside%20my%20house%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20them%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-500x889.jpg%5C%2