proach%20stray%20dogs%20and%20behave%20around%20them.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lack%20of%20understanding%20can%20lead%20to%20either%20the%20children%20hurting%20the%20animal%20or%20getting%20hurt%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20teach%20children%20how%20to%20safely%20and%20respectfully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F379789%2Fkind-hour-foundation-mouli-mehrotra-lucknow-art-education-animal-welfare-compassion-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteract%20with%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20creating%20positive%20experiences%20for%20both%20the%20animals%20and%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20programmes%20are%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20Pawsitivity%E2%80%99s%20mission%2C%20ensuring%20that%20children%20grow%20up%20with%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20street%20animals%20and%20a%20greater%20sense%20of%20empathy%20towards%20them.%20With%20Rimjhim%E2%80%99s%20connections%20as%20a%20former%20teacher%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20access%20various%20schools%20and%20run%20workshops%20that%20sensitise%20young%20minds%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20stray%20animals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rimjhim%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20faced%20many%20challenges%2C%20including%20financial%20difficulties%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20their%20passion%20for%20animal%20welfare%20has%20never%20faltered.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20pregnant%20during%20COVID%2C%20things%20were%20especially%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rimjhim%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20got%20a%20big%20order%20from%20an%20NGO%20that%20kept%20us%20going.%20It%20was%20during%20that%20time%20that%20I%20realised%20how%20much%20support%20we%20had%20from%20the%20animal%20welfare%20community.%20Our%20friend%20and%20supporter%2C%20the%20late%20Meenakshi%20Mahapatra%2C%20was%20truly%20an%20angel%20and%20helped%20us%20when%20we%20thought%20we%20would%20have%20to%20stop%20the%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawsitivity%20has%20seen%20significant%20growth%2C%20with%20revenue%20reaching%20Rs%2056%20lakh%20in%202023%20and%20projections%20for%202024%20set%20at%20Rs%2077%20lakh.%20The%20company%20has%20served%20over%201.5%20lakh%20customers%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F272456%2Fcat-cafe-studio-mumbai-lets-you-adopt-stray-animals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanimal%20feeders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20pet%20owners%20looking%20to%20better%20the%20safety%20of%20stray%20dogs%20and%20other%20animals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERimjhim%E2%80%99s%20focus%20remains%20on%20providing%20affordable%2C%20high-quality%20reflective%20collars%20to%20these%20groups%2C%20while%20also%20empowering%20women%20and%20supporting%20broader%20animal%20welfare%20efforts.%20The%20company%E2%80%99s%20pricing%20structure%20has%20made%20the%20collars%20accessible%20to%20many%20feeders%20who%20would%20otherwise%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20afford%20such%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Rimjhim%20Joshi%20Shende%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735655400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-12-at-12.36.43-PM-1733988743.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D388977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20started%20as%20a%20simple%20desire%20to%20help%20street%20dogs%20has%20transformed%20into%20'Pawsitivity'%2C%20a%20successful%20business%20led%20by%20Rimjhim%20Joshi%20Shende.%20Through%20affordable%20reflective%20and%20QR-enabled%20collars%2C%20she%20is%20making%20streets%20safer%20for%20animals%20while%20providing%20meaningful%20employment%20to%20women%20in%20need.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http