3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20he%20earns%20Rs%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20annually%20from%20the%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20only%20sell%20fruits%2C%20you%20can%20earn%20up%20to%20four%20to%20five%20lakh%20rupees%20per%20acre%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnshul%20also%20points%20out%20that%20dragon%20fruit%20farming%20requires%20only%20a%20one-time%20investment%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20per%20acre.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20homemade%20%3Cem%3Ejeevamrit%20%3C%2Fem%3E(natural%20liquid%20fertiliser%20made%20from%20cow%20dung)%20to%20boost%20fruit%20size%20and%20soil%20fertility.%20Using%20natural%20fertilisers%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20your%20input%20costs%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnshul%E2%80%99s%20model%20showcases%20the%20potential%20for%20sustainable%20and%20profitable%20farming.%20He%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20risks%20in%20agriculture%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20historical%20figures%20like%20Vasco%20da%20Gama%20and%20Columbus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20had%20not%20ventured%20into%20the%20unknown%2C%20we%20may%20not%20have%20discovered%20the%20sea%20route%20to%20India%20and%20discovered%20America.%20My%20father%20also%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20fear%20taking%20risks%2C%20you%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20success%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%2C%20Anshul%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20quips%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20son%20has%20proved%20that%20if%20you%20are%20dedicated%20and%20consistent%20in%20your%20efforts%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20achieve%20success.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20fear%20taking%20risks%20and%20continue%20to%20toil%20in%20the%20field%20by%20growing%20crops%20that%20they%20are%20comfortable%20with%2C%20even%20though%20they%20are%20unprofitable.%20Remember%20that%20if%20you%20sell%20one%20sack%20(50%20kg)%20of%20wheat%2C%20you%20earn%20the%20same%20amount%2